channel.title: Whats the latest version
channel.description:
Of internet explorer.. now i feel stupid somehow i managed to delete mine when i went through and cleaned my comp of its crap and well yes i managed to delete a file that did not say internet explorer and guess what i guess i needed that to run it.
I searched google and it said get the latest version 6, then it said get 7 no idea why it said latest version is 6 if 7 is better... so is there anything thats better than IE 7?
